parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can cause structural failure, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may exhibit unusual swaying or wobbling
especially at high speeds
and may produce unusual noises or vibrations. In severe cases
the frame may break or detach
causing loss of control or accidents.

the frame has visible rust or holes
